<!-- §9 What is [Product]? -->
<h2>What Is the Serene Sleep Spray?</h2>
<p>The Serene Sleep Spray is a 100ml pillow and room spray formulated with three essential oils specifically chosen for their sleep-promoting properties: lavender (anxiety relief), chamomile (gentle relaxation), and sandalwood (grounding). The formula is designed to be stain-free on fabric, non-toxic, and comes in eco-friendly packaging. It's not a sedative — it won't make you drowsy on its own — but it works as a behavioral anchor that trains your brain to recognize the scent as a cue to begin the sleep process.</p>

